The About page has been transformed into a premium, interactive experience.
- **Modern Design**: Used a rich, dark-themed hero section with high-quality imagery.
- **Animations**: Integrated `framer-motion` for smooth reveal animations as you scroll.
- **Content**: Added professionally written sections for "Our Story", "Philosophy", and "Stats".

### [NEW] [Contact Page](file:///d:/project/Funiture/Frontend/src/Pages/Contact.tsx)
